data.meta_description: Final Inventory of Lakes Report Annexespdf 1156 802 1658828398 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is an inventory of lakes in Nepal that includes 63 annexes, each detailing the lakes within a particular district. It provides a template for collecting data on lakes, including their general features, ecological characteristics, and biological features. The template collects information on the lakes' administrative information, physical structure, hydrological features, water quality, soil characteristics, and the plant and animal species found within and around each lake.
